I decided I have to tell her.

19:39.762 --> 19:42.015
I'm just gonna be honest,

19:39.762 --> 19:42.015
that's all.

19:42.015 --> 19:44.725
Yes, I'm nervous.

19:44.725 --> 19:47.311
Are you listening to me?

19:47.311 --> 19:49.730
Just-- Just put some soap

19:47.311 --> 19:49.730
on your finger.

19:49.730 --> 19:52.108
It'll slide right off.

19:52.108 --> 19:54.360
Well, then try axle grease.

19:54.360 --> 19:58.072
I'll call you back

19:54.360 --> 19:58.072
after I talk to her.

19:58.072 --> 20:00.658
Well...

20:00.658 --> 20:04.203
It's all taken care of.

20:04.203 --> 20:06.080
Everything's cool.

20:06.080 --> 20:07.999
What? What's cool?

20:07.999 --> 20:09.500
Elaine.

20:09.500 --> 20:11.460
What are you

20:09.500 --> 20:11.460
talking about?

20:11.460 --> 20:13.796
I just found a guy

20:11.460 --> 20:13.796
who's willing to pay $10,000

20:13.796 --> 20:15.798
for the apartment.

20:15.798 --> 20:17.675
You what? Get out!

20:17.675 --> 20:19.802
10,000?

20:17.675 --> 20:19.802
Cash!

20:19.802 --> 20:21.303
Who would pay that much?

20:21.303 --> 20:22.889
He's in the music business.

20:22.889 --> 20:25.391
Elaine would never borrow

20:22.889 --> 20:25.391
that much money. Kramer...

20:25.391 --> 20:26.934
my God, man.

20:26.934 --> 20:28.477
This is beautiful.

20:28.477 --> 20:29.896
I think

20:28.477 --> 20:29.896
I'm in the clear here.

20:29.896 --> 20:31.230
Elaine's not moving in.

20:31.230 --> 20:33.273
I don't have to confront her.

20:33.273 --> 20:35.776
She has no idea

20:33.273 --> 20:35.776
I never wanted her to move in.

20:35.776 --> 20:37.236
I'm golden.

20:37.236 --> 20:40.865
Well, occasionally,

20:37.236 --> 20:40.865
I like to help the humans.

20:45.703 --> 20:50.208
[LOUD ELECTRIC GUITAR PLAYING]

20:50.208 --> 20:53.252
ELAINE:

20:50.208 --> 20:53.252
Wow, you're right, that is loud.

20:53.252 --> 20:54.587
It's just unbelievable.

20:54.587 --> 20:56.839
They rehearse all the time?

20:54.587 --> 20:56.839
All the time!

20:56.839 --> 20:58.298
I've been up there six times.

20:58.298 --> 20:59.884
They refuse to stop.

20:59.884 --> 21:01.260
I can't live

20:59.884 --> 21:01.260
like this.

21:01.260 --> 21:02.887
I don't know what

21:01.260 --> 21:02.887
I'm gonna do.

21:02.887 --> 21:04.972
I'm headed for a breakdown.

21:02.887 --> 21:04.972
Can't you do something?

21:04.972 --> 21:07.141
I'm not going up.

21:04.972 --> 21:07.141
It stinks up there.

21:07.141 --> 21:08.267
Manny?

21:08.267 --> 21:13.397
[SPEAKING SPANISH]

21:13.397 --> 21:14.774
I'm not the one

21:13.397 --> 21:14.774
who said

21:14.774 --> 21:17.026
they could play

21:14.774 --> 21:17.026
till 11:00.

21:17.026 --> 21:18.652
He makes up

21:17.026 --> 21:18.652
his own rules.

21:18.652 --> 21:20.279
Boy, too bad. If I was up there,

21:20.279 --> 21:22.115
you'd never hear

21:20.279 --> 21:22.115
a peep out of me.

21:22.115 --> 21:24.033
I'm as quiet

21:22.115 --> 21:24.033
as a mouse.

21:24.033 --> 21:25.868
Hey.

21:25.868 --> 21:27.245
Oh!

21:27.245 --> 21:29.538
I love the one they do

21:27.245 --> 21:29.538
right after this one.

21:30.581 --> 21:32.332
I don't know.

21:32.332 --> 21:34.919
What do you do when a neighbor

21:32.332 --> 21:34.919
is making, like, a lot of noise

21:34.919 --> 21:36.295
at 3:00 in the morning?

21:36.295 --> 21:37.797
I mean, can you

21:36.295 --> 21:37.797
knock on someone's door

21:37.797 --> 21:39.215
and tell 'em to keep it down?

21:39.215 --> 21:41.008
You're really altering

21:39.215 --> 21:41.008
your whole self-image.

21:41.008 --> 21:42.718
I mean, what am I,

21:41.008 --> 21:42.718
Fred Mertz now?

21:42.718 --> 21:44.053
What's happening to me?

21:44.053 --> 21:46.639
Can I do this?

21:44.053 --> 21:46.639
Am I a shusher?

21:46.639 --> 21:48.348
I used to be a shushee.

21:48.348 --> 21:50.434
There's a lot of shushing

21:48.348 --> 21:50.434
going on in movie theaters.

21:50.434 --> 21:51.769
People are always shushing.

21:51.769 --> 21:54.563
Shh. Shh, shh. Shh!

21:54.563 --> 21:56.149
It doesn't work...

21:56.149 --> 21:57.733
Because nobody knows

21:56.149 --> 21:57.733
where a shush is coming from.

21:57.733 --> 21:59.152
They just hear a "shh!"

21:59.152 --> 22:00.903
Was that a shush?

21:59.152 --> 22:00.903
I think somebody shushed me.

22:00.903 --> 22:02.738
Some people you can't shush

22:00.903 --> 22:02.738
in a movie theater.

22:02.738 --> 22:04.907
There's always a certain group

22:02.738 --> 22:04.907
of people talking and talking.

22:04.907 --> 22:06.784
Everyone around them

22:04.907 --> 22:06.784
is shushing them, shushing them.

22:06.784 --> 22:09.411
They won't shush.

22:06.784 --> 22:09.411
They're the unshushables.

22:18.754 --> 22:21.966
[♪♪♪]
